List of features the game needs, one experiment for each:
- Collisions: balls, rectangles and walls.
- Game: Player controlled by keyboard/touch/accelerometer/wiimote.
- DONE FRP: Arrow growing up to the ceiling, dying when it touches the ceiling.
- DONE FRP: Arrow growing up to the ceiling, dying X secs after touching the ceiling.
- DONE FRP: Balls bouncing.
- FRP, Input: Balls bouncing, splitting in two on click.
- FRP, Collisions: Balls bouncing, splitting in two on collision with some arrows.
